description:
Hosted by Kaiser Chiefs frontman Ricky Wilson, this brand new music and comedy entertainment show puts celebrity teams to the test with music trivia, video parodies and unmissable performance battles. Nicole Scherzinger and Tinie Tempah take charge as team captains and comedians Katherine Ryan and Joel Dommet join the fun as regular panellists.




Bring the Noise - Season 1, Episode 1



Former Doctor Who star David Tennant and Spandau Ballet's Martin Kemp are this week's guests, with two teams put to the test during rounds including music trivia, spoof video parodies and musical performance battles.



Original Air Date: 22-Oct-2015
